{"tid":2129741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"被低估的好領隊　朗拿度：他是個智者和好人","createTime":"2020-07-28T21:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T08:49:15.000Z","uid":165817,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bddd3b1cbb22f9a8c61ac398b1f1d5419e4c956c","tid":2129741,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T21:46:11.000Z","msg":"「我在國際米蘭遇過很多優秀的領隊，當中尤其是盧基施蒙尼令我印象非常深刻。他是一個好人、一個心腸非常好的人。他營造出了家一樣的氛圍，在他麾下踢球很舒服。」<br />\n- 森莫蘭奴<br />\n<br />\n「盧基施蒙尼就像是球員們的父親，他建立出一支非常強大的球隊，讓所有人都覺得自己就是大家庭中的一份子。我們在每一場比賽都表現出最好一面，也贏了歐洲足協盃，遺憾的是沒有跟隨盧基施蒙尼贏得意甲冠軍。」<br />\n- J.辛尼迪<br />\n<br />\n「盧基施蒙尼對我來說不只是一名教練，更是一個智者和一個好人。他不會逼球員做某些事情，而是會解釋為何做這件事如此重要。他是我心中的大師，我會永遠記得他那些寶貴的建議。他教導我的東西，比他想像中還多。」<br />\n- 朗拿度<br />\n<br />\nLuigi Simoni<br />\n(1939-2020)<br />\nRest in peace<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc3xcCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foc3xcCE.jpg&h=a72a22ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7961f9bb576ab40c5686e0185e02d5d29a6682a2","tid":2129741,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c50f07ea47d5470958870508bcdd8f57eafb00","tid":2129741,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:47:26.000Z","msg":"都估到，無啦啦搵個古人吹奏，實出左事，等於報紙上叫得孝順仔，好爸爸，都奶晒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f9b37770331d8801f30e3b1dd8bbedf8542a7c","tid":2129741,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:07:50.000Z","msg":"以前係馬體會果件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm